---
---
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 border-y border-gray-200">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">

    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Built for real businesses</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        These are real projects with booking, conversion, and ad-tracking systems implemented.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <a href="https://artilate.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition">
        <picture>
          <source type="image/webp" srcset="/proof/artilate-hero-480.webp 480w, /proof/artilate-hero-768.webp 768w" sizes="(min-width:768px) 33vw, 100vw"/>
          <img src="/proof/artilate-hero-768.webp" class="h-44 w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" alt="Artilate Chocolate"/>
        </picture>
        <div class="p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">E-commerce · Alberta</p>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-gray-900">Artilate Chocolate</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">Conversion-focused purchase flow and event tracking tied to real orders.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://refreshedexterior.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/refresh-exteriors.png" class="h-44 w-full object-cover object-top" loading="lazy" alt="Refresh Exteriors"/>
        <div class="p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Home Services · Calgary</p>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-gray-900">Refresh Exteriors</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">New website live in 2 weeks — first new customer within 7 days.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://gaplets.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition">
        <picture>
          <source type="image/webp" srcset="/proof/gaplets-hero-480.webp 480w, /proof/gaplets-hero-768.webp 768w" sizes="(min-width:768px) 33vw, 100vw"/>
          <img src="/proof/gaplets-hero-768.webp" class="h-44 w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" alt="Gaplets"/>
        </picture>
        <div class="p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Scheduling SaaS</p>
          <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-gray-900">Gaplets</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">Appointment flow, cancellation recovery, and automated client replacement.</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <a href="/proof" class="text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 font-medium transition">
        View all projects →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
